#: app/inventory/templates/inventory/create_batch.html:84
msgid ""
"Submitting this manifest will update the live medical inventory and "
"initialize chronological audit logs for HIPAA compliance."
msgstr "Gudbinta warbixintan waxay cusboonaysiin doontaa kaydka daawada tooska ah waxayna bilaabi doontaa diiwaanka xisaab xirka."

#: app/inventory/templates/inventory/create_batch.html:90
msgid "Add Stock Batch"
msgstr "Kudar Dufcad cusub"

#: app/inventory/templates/inventory/create_batch.html:99
msgid "Supply Chain Validation"
msgstr "Xaqiijinta Silsiladda Saadka"

#: app/inventory/templates/inventory/create_batch.html:101
msgid ""
"Batch tracking is critical for preventing the distribution of expired "
"pharmaceuticals. Ensure all expiry dates are verified against the "
"physical consignment labels before system entry."
msgstr "Raadraaca dufcaddaha ayaa muhiim u ah ka hortagga qaybinta daawooyinka dhacay. Hubi in dhammaan taariikhaha dhicitaanka la xaqiijiyay ka hor inta aan la gelin nidaamka."

#: app/inventory/templates/inventory/create_batch.html:105
msgid "Fiscal Impact"
msgstr "Saamaynta Maaliyadeed"

#: app/inventory/templates/inventory/create_batch.html:107
msgid ""
"The patient billing rate entered here will be used to generate automated "
"invoices in the Billing & Finance module for this specific batch."
msgstr "Qiimaha Bukaanka la galiyay halkan waxaa loo isticmaali doonaa in si toos ah loogu abuuro qaansheegta qaybta Maaliyadda."

